{"tid":561538,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"[支那人柒少陣啦好嗎]小米投票風波！萬普拉斯CEO 抽水抽著火水","createTime":"2018-02-15T05:47:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-17T07:01:14.000Z","uid":55951,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"6b473bce3ba55c2fb3ff748f7b9e620bdddd018e","tid":561538,"uid":55951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T05:47:18.000Z","msg":"還記得幾日前我們報導過，因為投票結果不符小米期望，竟然刪除了 Twitter 有關 MIUI 9 和 Android One 的選舉。事件經過外國傳媒報導後，小米慘被網民恥笑，認為他們輸打贏要和充滿中國特色。事隔幾日萬普拉斯CEO 裴宇嘗試抽水，不過卻抽著火水。<br />\n<br />\n一名唔識死的萬普拉斯工程師日前竟然在 Twitter 發起相似的選舉，讓網民在自家 OxygenOS 和原生 Android 投票二選一。起初結果一面倒傾向 OxygenOS，裴宇可能以為勝算在握，於是加把嘴發 Tweet 叫工程師千萬不要刪帖，以為可以乘機抽小米水。<br />\n<br />\n點知裴宇慶祝得太早，網民喺佢發 Tweet 後投票意向大逆轉，超過 1 萬名網民投票的結果顯示，有 58% 喜歡原生 Android，傾向 OxygenOS 的只有 42%。萬普拉斯的系統早前爆出不少私隱相關問題，網民投票選擇原生 Android 無可厚非，幸好該名萬普拉斯工程師有聽腦細話，未有將投票刪除並且留言說會聆聽網民意見，起碼避免進一步發生公關災難。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/15/134615_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F15%2F134615_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=58a10538&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4988/210126/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.eprice.com.hk%2Fmobile%2Ftalk%2F4988%2F210126%2F&d=%2Ff3dVIMZAgN3cVdO%2BLpXNLDFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=161503da\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4988/210126/</a>"},{"pid":"1c82e700bf22221a478769fc100c523befbcb0d1","tid":561538,"uid":4285,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T06:06:35.000Z","msg":"大家都係支那人"},{"pid":"ba378026e3261bd2942b674755df1e3a55f7fb32","tid":561538,"uid":37524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T06:10:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e4b137c7e156ba9f57cca5a5ba4d4184ac322df","tid":561538,"uid":3773,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":